    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for something dependable that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you! It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
