      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering an exceptional balance of performance, reliability, and sophisticated presentation. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical integrity and roadworthiness. Both the interior and exterior reflect a history of attentive care, demonstrating the vehicle's sustained quality and enduring appeal. For the discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-caliber automobile that represents a significant value proposition, this remains a premier choice. Available for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 34900.0,
