    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s been super well-maintained and still has that smooth, reliable feel you\u2019re looking for in a daily driver. It\u2019s in great shape and ready for its next adventure with a new owner! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
