    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example retains its factory 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M-differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement, addressing common chassis fatigue points. The suspension geometry remains taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for precise lateral transients. While the finish shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car for those prioritizing mechanical excellence and analog feedback.",
